Squizzy::

She was thinking about what LadyHawk had said.  She glanced at the 
external monitor and saw that there were two bots at the ship's 
entrance.  She sighed and walked out of the lab.  She had a lot on 
her mind and couldn't shake the feeling that LadyHawk was hiding 
something.  She finally got to the entrance and opened the hatch.
"What's going on here?" She looked down and saw a bot in bad need of 
care.(LIFE)  She looked at the other one. "If you can carry him, I'll 
take you to the CR lab and we can get you both fixed up. By the way, 
I'm Squizzy. Pleased to meet you. Now hurry, that one looks like he's 
got one foot in the matrix already."
